comments: Gibson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dinwiddie (BKN) and does not deliver contact.

Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ntilikina (NYK) and does not deliver contact.  He briefly places two hands on him but disengages without affecting his ability to defend the play.
Dinwiddie (BKN) gathers the ball and takes three steps.
Ntilikina (NYK) makes marginal contact to the body of Dinwiddie (BKN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Dinwiddie (BKN) and Morris Sr. (NYK) engage and disengage off ball.
Temple (BKN) makes incidental contact to the arm of Ellington (NYK) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes contact to the arm of Harris (BKN) at the end of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Ntilikina (NYK) and Allen (BKN) engage and disengage off ball.
Harris (BKN) gathers the ball and jump stops on both feet.  He then legally takes a step before releasing his shot attempt at the rim.
Gibson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dinwiddie (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes marginal contact with Dinwiddie (BKN) on the perimeter and does not hook him or otherwise dislodge him from his defensive position.
Gibson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dinwiddie (BKN) and firms up on his left foot.
Gibson (NYK) commits a loose ball foul on Allen (BKN).
Gibson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dinwiddie (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (BKN) makes marginal contact to the body of Morris Sr. (NYK) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) and Allen (BKN) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Gibson (NYK) gets his hand on the ball and any contact prior to the held ball is considered incidental.
Prince (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Randle's (NYK) shot at the rim.
Ntilikina (NYK) commits a take foul on Harris (BKN).
Prince (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Ellington's (BKN) shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes marginal contact with Randle (NYK) during the rebound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Randle's (NYK) shot attempt.
